{"tid":647649,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★無錢 IT知識不足？9成學校網站無用加密系統","createTime":"2018-04-30T04:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T10:59:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"61215b842b6c08fdf197b415e4960110be2657a9","tid":647649,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"學校資訊公司AiTLE委託資訊科技服務公司進行「全港學校網站安全普查」，以電腦系統掃描方式，調查超過1000間中小學管理網站使用加密系統「HTTPS」的情況，發現約90%本地學校網站及內聯網沒有使用加密系統。調查亦發現只有57%受訪者認為此舉是「重要」及「很重要」，但學校主要面對技術、金錢及時間問題而放棄加密。<br />\n<br />\n資訊科技教育領袖協會主席黃健威指，學校不是沒有資源，因為安裝加密程式是可以免費，而是對資訊科技意識不足，例如尋找伺服器設定、或分辨SSL憑證的知識，<span style=\"color: red;\">一般校內技術人員都不清楚，而學校抱着「學生資料咁簡單，外洩都無太問題啫」的心態。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180430/bkn-20180430114443331-0430_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180430%2Fbkn-20180430114443331-0430_00822_001.html&d=o%2B%2Ft6ZNhMNaLeTnMtccsFdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=3f681eed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180430/bkn-20180430114443331-0430_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"da6db958112bea8e2b217d9f34f021fe6caa70bf","tid":647649,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"HK No IT"},{"pid":"6f2ef2089037853c44cba4507c637c6ddef03d08","tid":647649,"uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:32:44.000Z","msg":"因為安裝加密程式是可以免費<br />\n因為安裝加密程式是可以免費<br />\n因為安裝加密程式是可以免費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IT Free is not enough !!<br />\n<br />\nNeed Gift</span>"},{"pid":"5a8ef7d8ee5153016dc0106ca8e85f4e4134e86d","tid":647649,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:34:29.000Z","msg":"個web都唔係自己起<br />\n鬼識整咩"},{"pid":"870df5a41d29ed0fa021ebc2f9985117ad98652e","tid":647649,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2